# --- Layer8Culture content engine ---

# Generated visuals (regenerated by the workflow; do not version)
# Covers images, carousel slides, reel mp4s, and reel cover frames. The
# generate workflow force-adds this dir into the approval PR for review.
assets/generated/*
!assets/generated/.gitkeep

# Per-day generated PNGs in the queue (keep .json / .summary.md / .gitkeep)
queue/*.png

# Transient approval-PR body built by scripts/build_pr_preview.py (workflow only)
pr-body.md

# Never commit large binaries / installers (GitHub rejects >100MB)
*.exe

# Keep brand assets in assets/library/ and assets/fonts/ (NOT ignored):
#   library: layer8-wordmark.png
#   fonts:   SpaceGrotesk-Variable.ttf, Inter-Variable.ttf (+ OFL licenses)
# Style-reference images were removed — generation relies on the prompt, and
# branded headline typography is composited per brand/visual-style.md.

# --- Python ---
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.venv/
venv/
.env
*.env

# --- OS / editor noise ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/

# --- Local ops helper (contains VM connection details; do not commit) ---
set-instagram-creds.ps1
set-postiz-apikey.ps1
